  <thing id="eqValenrid" name="Valenar riding horse" description="Famed as the fastest horses in all of Khorvaire, these animals are bred by the elves of Valenar to carry warriors across the battle field. A mounted Valenar elf is able to speed into the thick of combat, strike, and dart away.{br}Speed Per Hour - Speed Per Day - Normal Load (lb.) - Heavy Load (lb.) - Push/Drag (lb.){br}6 miles - 60 miles - 175 - 350 - 875{br}{br}Valenar Riding Horse{br}Large fey beast  (mount){br}Level 2 Skirmisher XP 125  {b}Initiative{/b} +7 {b}Senses{/b} Perception +3; low-light vision{br}{b}HP{/b} 37; {b}Bloodied{/b} 18{br}{b}AC{/b} 18; {b}Fortitude{/b} 14, {b}Reflex{/b} 16, {b}Will{/b} 14{br}{b}Speed{/b} 10 {b}Kick{/b} (standard, at-will) +7 vs AC; 1d6+6 damage.  {b}Nimble Beast{/b} (move; encounter) The Valenar riding horse shifts 2 squares. {b}Swift Steed{/b} (minor; while mounted by a friendly rider of 2nd level or higher; encounter) * {b}Mount{/b}The Valenar riding horse gains a +4 bonus to speed until the end of its next turn.{b}Alignment{/b} Unaligned{b} Languages{/b} -{br}{b}Skills{/b} Endurance +7{br}{b}Str{/b} 14 (+3)  {b}Dex{/b} 18 (+5)  {b}Wis{/b} 14 (+3){br}{b}Con{/b} 13 (+2)  {b}Int{/b} 2 (-3)  {b}Cha{/b} 9 (0)" compset="Mount">
