  <thing id="eqWarcro" name="War crodlu" description="A crodlu is a large, flightless drake with a beak and weak, clawed forelimbs that can be used to manipulate small objects. It is a tough and aggressive hunter in the wild. When trained, it makes an excellent war mount.{br}Speed per Hour - Speed per Day - Normal Load (lb.) - Heavy Load (lb.) - Push/Drag (lb.){br}4 miles - 40 miles - 200 - 400 - 1000{br}{br}War Crodlu{br}Large natural beast (mount, reptile){br}Level 5 Brute XP 200{b}HP{/b} 76; {b}Bloodied{/b} 38{b}Initiative{/b} +5{br}{b}AC{/b} 17, {b}Fortitude{/b} 19, {b}Reflex{/b} 17, {b}Will{/b} 15{b}Perception{/b}+3{br}{b}Speed{/b} 8{br}Standard Actions {b}Beak{/b} * {b}At-Will{/b}{i}Attack:{/i} Melee 1 (one creature); +10 vs. AC{i}Hit:{/i} 2d6 + 3 damage. {b}Claws{/b} * {b}At-Will{/b}{i}Attack:{/i} Melee 1 (one creature); +10 vs. AC{i}Hit:{/i} 1d8 + 4 damage. {b}Pounce{/b} * {b}At-Will{/b}{i}Effect:{/i} The crodlu can move its speed. Whether or not it moves, it can use beak and claws, making each attack against the same target. If both attacks hit, the target also falls prone.Triggered Actions {b}Pouncing Mount{/b} (mount) * {b}Encounter{/b}{i}Trigger:{/i} The crodlu charges an enemy while mounted by a friendly rider of 5th level or higher.{i}Effect (No Action):{/i} The crodlu&apos;s rider can make a melee basic attack as a free action against the target of the crodlu&apos;s charge.{b}Str{/b} 20 (+7)  {b}Dex{/b} 16 (+5)  {b}Wis{/b} 13 (+3){br}{b}Con{/b} 16 (+5)  {b}Int{/b} 3 (-2)  {b}Cha{/b} 8 (+1){b}Alignment{/b} Unaligned{b} Languages{/b} -" compset="Mount">
