  <thing id="eqHorseWar" name="Warhorse" description="Normal Load - Heavy Load - Max.Drag{br}262 lb. - 525 lb. - 1,312 lb.{br}{br}Warhorse{br}Large natural beast  (mount){br}Level 3 Brute XP 150  {b}Initiative{/b} +3 {b}Senses{/b} Perception +8; low-light vision{br}{b}HP{/b} 58; {b}Bloodied{/b} 29{br}{b}AC{/b} 17; {b}Fortitude{/b} 16, {b}Reflex{/b} 14, {b}Will{/b} 14{br}{b}Speed{/b} 8 {b}Kick{/b} (standard, at-will) +6 vs AC; 1d6+5 damage.  {b}Trample{/b} (standard, at-will) The warhorse can move up to its speed and enter enemies&apos; spaces. This movement provokes opportunity attacks, and the warhorse must end its move in an unoccupied space. When it enters an enemy&apos;s space, the warhorse makes a trample attack; +4 vs Reflex; 1d6+6 damage, and the target is knocked prone.  {b}Charger{/b} (while mounted by a friendly rider of 3rd level or higher with the mounted combat feat; at-will) * {b}Mount{/b}The warhorse grants its rider a +5 bonus to damage rolls on charge attacks.{b}Alignment{/b} Unaligned{b} Languages{/b} -{br}{b}Str{/b} 21 (+6)  {b}Dex{/b} 14 (+3)  {b}Wis{/b} 14 (+3){br}{b}Con{/b} 18 (+5)  {b}Int{/b} 2 (-3)  {b}Cha{/b} 10 (+1)" compset="Mount">
