  <thing id="eqTrDisBea" name="Displacer Beast (Fey Beast Companion)" description="Although feared throughout the Feywild as a cunning and deadly predator, a displacer beast can be tamed by someone wise in the ways of the spirits. You have managed to achieve this rapport, taking special pride in the wide-eyed stares that you and your companion receive during your travels.{br}{br}{b}Trained Displacer Beast - Medium fey beast (fey beast companion){/b}{br}{b}Initiative{/b} equal to yours {b}Senses{/b} Perception equal to yours +2, Low-light vision{br}{b}HP{/b} your Bloodied Value{b}{br}AC{/b} 15 + your level; {b}Fortitude{/b} 11 + your level, {b}Reflex{/b} 15 + your level, {b}Will{/b} 15 + your level{br}{b}Speed{/b} 8 {br}{b}TRAITS{/b} {br}{b}Displacement (illusion; Aura 1){/b} Allies gain a +1 power bonus to all defenses while in the aura.{br}{b}STANDARD ACTIONS{/b} {br}{b}Tentacle (illusion; At-will; basic){/b} {i}Attack:{/i} Melee 1 (one creature); your level +5 vs AC {i}Hit:{/i} 1d8 + one-half your level damage, and the displacer beast gains partial concealment until the end of its next turn. {i}Level 21:{/i} 2d8 + one-half your level damage. {br}{b}Str{/b} 15 {b}Dex{/b} 20 {b}Wis{/b} 16 {b}Con{/b} 16 {b}Int{/b} 2 {b}Cha{/b} 6" compset="Mount">
