  <thing id="eqTrYouOwl" name="Young Owlbear (Fey Beast Companion)" description="Young owlbears are valued by the Feywild&apos;s goblins, who train the beasts to serve as guardians. Perhaps you freed your new companion from a goblin trap or beat it into submission after the goblins sicced it on you. However you two came together, the owlbear now fights for you. {br}{br}{b}Trained Young Owlbear - Medium fey beast (fey beast companion){/b}{br}{b}Initiative{/b} equal to yours {b}Senses{/b} Perception equal to yours +2, Darkvision{br}{b}HP{/b} your Bloodied Value{b} {br}AC{/b} 13 + your level; {b}Fortitude{/b} 15 + your level, {b}Reflex{/b} 11 + your level, {b}Will{/b} 15 + your level{br}{b}Speed{/b} 6 {br}{b}TRAITS{/b} {br}{b}Ferocious Companion (Aura 1){/b} Allies gain a +2 power bonus to damage rolls against enemies in the aura. {br}{b}STANDARD ACTIONS{/b} {br}{b}Claw (At-will; basic){/b} {i}Attack:{/i} Melee 1 (one creature); Your level +5 vs AC {i}Hit:{/i} 1d12 + one-half your level damage. {i}Level 21:{/i} 2d12 + one-half your level damage. {br}{b}Str{/b} 20 {b}Dex{/b} 12 {b}Wis{/b} 14 {b}Con{/b} 17 {b}Int{/b} 2 {b}Cha{/b} 6" compset="Mount">
